data.description: SELLERS WILL CONTRIBUTE $10,000 IN ANY WAY MONEY WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER! 4 bedroom 3 bathroom all brick home Craftsman style home on 1+ acre lot in Yellow River Plantation! This 2674 sq ft home has an open concept split floorplan that buyers have come to expect. As you enter the home, you are greeted by a large 25x5 foyer, with a home office to the right and a large formal dining room to the left. At the end of the foyer, you are greeted by a spacious living room with ceiling fan and access to sliding glass door access to that back yard. The living room is connect to the spacious kitchen, perfect for entertaining! The kitchen offers all stainless steel appliances (refrigerator, smooth top range, dishwasher, microwave), island, pantry, and plenty of cabinetry. There is an indoor laundry room just off the kitchen with a washer and dryer that stay with the home. The oversized master bedroom has a tray ceiling, crown, and fan. The master can easily accommodate a king bed and other furniture. The master bathroom is complete with double vanity, corner tub, linen closet, water closet and walk-in closet. The other side of the home offers 3 additional bedrooms and two additional full bathrooms. The two car side entry garage offers plenty of space to store vehicles and more. Enjoy the 23x8 covered front porch, perfect for your rocking chairs. The home has a large front yard and side-entry driveway which guides you to the privacy fenced backyard. The backyard is even larger than the front, and offers room for both boat or RV storage. The backyard has additional features to enjoy, such as 12x12 patio for grilling, 40x10 raised garden bed, and 39x36 chicken coop with professionally built coop with 12 laying boxes! Yellow River Plantation offers nature trails, two stocked fishing ponds, picnic areas for residents to enjoy. So, don't miss out on your opportunity to make this amazing property YOUR new home. Schedule your showing today!
